# Alluding
ЁЯСЙ Referring to something indirectly, without mentioning it clearly or openly.
## Simple explanation
When you allude to something, you hint at it, but you donтАЩt say it directly.
Example sentences
*She was alluding to a problem at work without explaining it clearly.
*The speaker kept alluding to past mistakes but never named them.
*He smiled, alluding to a surprise he didnтАЩt want to reveal yet.

